text: Patrick Vibert-Vichet (born 3 February 1959) is a French rower. He competed at the 1984 Summer Olympics and the 1992 Summer Olympics. ==References== Category:1959 births Category:Living people Category:French male rowers Category:Olympic rowers of France Category:Rowers at the 1984 Summer Olympics Category:Rowers at the 1992 Summer Olympics Category:Sportspeople from Haute- Savoie
